///////////////////////////////////////////
// trap.sv
//
// Written: David_Harris@hmc.edu 9 January 2021
// Modified: dottolia@hmc.edu 14 April 2021: Add support for vectored interrupts
//
// Purpose: Handle Traps: Exceptions and Interrupts
