                      LoadMisalignedFaultM | StoreAmoMisalignedFaultM |
                      BothInstrPageFaultM | LoadPageFaultM | StoreAmoPageFaultM |
                      BreakpointFaultM | EcallFaultM |
                      LoadAccessFaultM | StoreAmoAccessFaultM;
  // coverage on
